## Data Fetching & API Architecture

### ‚úÖ **Data Fetching Strategy**

**GET Requests (Read Operations)**
- ‚úÖ **Server Components**: Use direct database/API calls in server components
- ‚úÖ **No API Routes**: Skip Next.js API routes for read operations
- ‚úÖ **Caching**: Leverage Next.js built-in caching and streaming

**Non-GET Requests (Write Operations)**  
- ‚úÖ **API Route Handlers**: Create Next.js API routes for mutations
- ‚úÖ **TanStack Query**: Use mutations for client-side state management
- ‚úÖ **Error Handling**: Centralized error handling in API routes

